INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (5,1001007,'2014-02-25 18:25:00','2014-02-25 18:25:00','<h1 class=\"text-center\">Welcome to Blevins Dentistry<br /> in Mullins, SC<br /> <small>Also Serving Aynor, Florence, Loris, Marion, Myrtle Beach and the Surrounding Areas</small></h1> \r\n\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n    <p>Are you searching for a new dentist in Mullins, Aynor, Loris, Marion, Myrtle Beach or the surrounding area? Are you experiencing dental problems that may require cosmetic or restorative dental work? Are you looking for the best dentist in the area, but aren’t quite sure where to turn?</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>At Blevins Dentistry, <strong>we understand that choosing a dental team you can trust for your oral health and well-being is no easy task</strong>.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-8 text-center\">\r\n      <div class=\"video-container\">\r\n        <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=647_D1-vems\" data-lity>\r\n          <span class=\"fa-stack fa-2x\">\r\n            <i class=\"fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x\"></i>\r\n            <i class=\"fa fa-play fa-stack-1x fa-inverse\"></i>\r\n          </span>\r\n          <div class=\"shader\"></div>\r\n          <img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/Screen-Shot-2016-04-26-at-1.08.18-PM-1024x558.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2016-04-26 at 1.08.18 PM\" width=\"625\" height=\"341\" class=\"size-large wp-image-4286\" />\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p><small><em>More about Blevins Dentistry</em></small></p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3979\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1-1-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3979\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/4.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3973\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/4-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3973\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/5-1.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-3980\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/5-1-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-3980\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-md-6 col-lg-3\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/blevins-building.jpg\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-4269\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/blevins-building-300x189.jpg\" alt=\"blevins-building\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4269\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1rem;\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-10 offset-lg-1\">\r\n    <p>However, from the moment you walk into our office, you’ll notice things are a bit different around here. We’re not a stuffy dental office with no personalities; just the opposite in fact. You’ll find our entire team is full of joy and laughter, which many of our patients say makes them feel right at home each time they walk through our doors.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>In addition to a fun and relaxing environment, caring about patients also involves recommending the best treatments for every situation. What you are looking for in a dentist may be quite different from someone else, so <strong>Dr. Blevins takes the time to sit down with each and every patient to get to know them and what they are looking to accomplish with their smile.</strong></p> \r\n\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n        <p>Our initial examination and X-rays appointment is always commented on by our patients as the most thorough they have ever received. The digital 3D X-rays, photos, and oral cancer exam are just a few of the services we provide at that visit. Patients appreciate the time taken, care and communication by our doctor and team.</p>\r\n\r\n        <p>As Dr. Blevins saw the increasing needs of the baby boom generation, several years ago he acquired the technology and the training to place and restore dental implants. Implant dentistry provides a comfortable and affordable way to replace a single tooth or an entire arch of teeth.</p>\r\n\r\n       <p>Another service that many patients utilize is our same-day crowns and veneers using CEREC technology. Patients appreciate the convenience of this method over traditional multi-appointment treatment. We value our patients\' time, and they value our excellent care and five-star service. </p>\r\n\r\n       <p>Whether it’s dental implants, porcelain veneers, or any other procedure we offer, you’re in the right place! So if you’re looking for a dentist in Mullins, Loris, Aynor, Dillon, Latta, Marion, Conway, North Myrtle & Myrtle Beach, Longs, Little River or Horry County, contact our office today to schedule your appointment.</p> \r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n        <img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/new-patient-special-exam-xrays-654x1024.jpg\" alt=\"new-patient-special-exam-xrays\" width=\"625\" height=\"979\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-4372\" />\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2017-09-27 17:52:25','2017-09-27 17:52:25','',0,'http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),(7,1001007,'2014-02-25 18:25:06','2014-02-25 18:25:06','','Blog','','publish','o