<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/crooked-teeth-square.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/crooked-teeth-square-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4630 rounded-circle\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n    <p>Are your teeth crooked, or not quite as white as they used to be?</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>Do you often have a “closed mouth smile” because you’re self-conscious others will notice that your smile isn’t perfect?</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>That’s no way to live, especially when you can do something about it!</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>Dr. Todd Blevins is a highly-acclaimed cosmetic dentist practicing in Mullins, South Carolina. <strong>People drive from all across South Carolina to have their dream smile created by Dr. Blevins at our practice.</strong></p> \r\n\r\n    <p>Below you’ll see a link to our testimonials page, as well as a link to our smile gallery showcasing some of Dr. Blevins work:</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/testimonials/\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block\">Testimonials <i class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/smile-gallery/\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block\">Smile Gallery <i class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n    <h3>Back up...so what is a smile makeover anyway?</h3>\r\n\r\n    <p>A smile makeover is the process of improving one’s smile through one or more cosmetic dentistry procedures such as teeth whitening, veneers, white fillings, Lumineers, crowns, dental caps, or bridges.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>It’s a lot like building or remodeling your house actually.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p><strong>You’ll sit down and talk face to face with Dr. Blevins regarding why you want a smile makeover,</strong> your frustrations with your current smile, any questions or concerns you may have, and so much more.</p>\r\n\r\n    <p>You tell him what you are looking to achieve, and he uses his vast knowledge, experience, tools, and modern technology to create your dream smile.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>Simply put, Dr Blevins will be your smile artist. He will assess your current smile and talk through your options for attaining your dream smile!</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/doctor-patient-square.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/doctor-patient-square-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4037 rounded-circle\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/question-square.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/question-square-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4631 rounded-circle\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n    <h3>Sounds great, but how am I going to pay for this smile makeover?</h3>\r\n\r\n    <p>Many cosmetic dentists want to dodge the money question, but reality is that it’s an important part of the decision making process and has to be considered.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>One of the reasons that many patients don’t have the smile of their dreams is because they think they can’t afford it. We definitely understand your concern, but by partnering with CareCredit, we’ve got you covered.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p><strong>You can finance the smile of your dreams (in some cases with 0% interest for up to 24 months)</strong> so that Dr. Blevins gets compensated for his excellent work and you get the smile you’ve always wanted.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>It’s truly a win-win situation.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3>Let’s recap:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You’re not satisfied with your smile</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>Dr. Blevins is one of the most accomplished cosmetic dentists in the area, and people drive from all around South Carolina to see him for their smile makeovers.</li>\r\n\r\n	<li>You’re already on our practice website right now</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>And best of all…</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We’ve already mentioned how you can afford this, so finances aren’t holding you back anymore.</p> \r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-8\">\r\n    <h2>What are you waiting for?</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>If you’re the man or woman in the family pictures that “never smiles” then it’s time to change that. Schedule your smile makeover consultation (no obligation, and definitely no sales pressure whatsoever), visit with Dr. Blevins, and then hopefully you’ll choose Blevins Dentistry to help you with the smile of your dreams.</p> \r\n\r\n    <p>Give us a call today, or fill out the form right here on our website to schedule your consultation.</p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\r\n    <a href=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/smiling-woman-square-1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/smiling-woman-square-1-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-4098 rounded-circle\" /></a>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>','Smile Makeovers','','publish','closed','closed','','smile-makeovers','','','2017-08-29 04:07:06','2017-08-29 04:07:06','',0,'http://www.blevinsdentistry.com/?page_id=4627',0,'page','',0),(4630,1001007,'2017-08-29 04:05:02','2017-08-29 04:05:02','','crooked-teeth-square','','inherit','open','closed','','crooked-teeth-squa